ARTICLE.TITLE: US intel: Russia acting against Biden; China opposes Trump
ARTICLE.TEXT: NEW YORK (AP) — For all the secrecy and speculation that typically surrounds the search for a vice presidential candidate, the decision rarely sways an election. But ahead of Joe Biden's imminent announcement, this year could be different.
